  <h4>18. Tell us about two semantic tags are included in HTML5 version ?</h4>
  <p class=" text-justify">
          <b>Ans:</b> The &lt;article&gt; and &lt;section&gt; tags are two new tags that are included in the HTML5. Articles can be composed of multiple sections that can have multiple articles and
