  </p><br>
           <h4>19.What is &lt;figure&gt; in HTML5 ?
            </h4>
           <p class=" text-justify">
                  <b>Ans:</b> This tag represents a piece of self-contained flow content and it is mostly used as a single unit as a reference the main flow of the document.
                                                       
  </p><br>
  <h4>20. Tell us two benefits of HTML5 Web Storage ?</h4>
  <p class=" text-justify">
          <b>Ans:</b> Two main benefits of HTML5 Web Storage are: <br>
